::Striker/DeathStorm::

Striker looks at Key and Liono. "I'll leave you two to your .... 
amusements." He says, grins, and flies off.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DeathStorm sighs. This was getting nowhere.

"This is getting us nowhere. I explained to you why I pulled my gun 
out." He growls softly. "I need to speak to your leader. If you would 
be so kind as to show me the way..."
